      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Conway''s game of life is the most well-known

    cellular automata,
    that made the field popular in

    the first place (even though there were cellular

    automata
    before it). It consists of a 2d grid were

    each cell looks at his direct
    neighbours including

    diagonals. This is called the Moore Neighbourhood,

    and
    it is the most commonly used neighbourhood.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
