  m_text: 'These small structures tend to emerge frequently,

    so if you draw
    some random lines, you will probably

    see some gliders and small oscillators.
    Try it out!

    I have also put an example of a Gosper''s glider gun,

    which
    is a structure that makes gliders infinitely.'
