  m_text: 'The first two examples are:

    Replicator - B1357/S1357. Start by drawing
    anything

    in the center of the grid and see as it turns into infinite

    copies
    of itself.

    Life without Death - B3/S012345678. In this automaton,

    nothing
    can die, which leads to facsinating patterns

    and behaviors. Also called
    "Inkspot" and "Flakes".'
