      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Wireworld, like game of life, is a 2d automaton that

    uses the moore
    neighbourhood. Unlike life, Wireworld

    has 4 states: empty (black), electron
    head (blue),

    electron tail (red) and conductor (yellow). The rules

    are
    very simple: empty stays empty, elcetron heads

    turns to electron tails,
    tails turn to conducrtors

    and a conductor with 1 or 2 neighbouring heads

    turns
    into a head, and stays a conductor otherwise.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
