  m_text: 'There isn''t really one name for this family of cellular

    automata,
    but phrases like "similar to life" or life-like

    work. automata from this
    family are notated by

    Bx/Sy where x is the numbers 0-8 which make a

    cell
    be born, and so is y for survival. As said before,

    Conway''s game is notated
    B3/S23.'
