  m_text: 'The last two examples use unique neighbourhoods,

    I found them by
    fiddling around with the program.

    Smaller life - B2/S21 which uses the Von
    Neumann neighborhood, the imediate neighbours, not

    including diagonals (so
    only looks at 4 cells).'
