  m_text: "these aren't any just normal squares, they're alive!\nevery now and then,
    they may die, or birth new ones.\nthis all happens according to certain rules,
    dictating\nwhen an alive cell will survive, and when a dead\ncell will be born.
    usually dead cells are white and \nalive cells are black."
